author: @mari-ka7873
text:
Billboard Japanのインタビュー記事を読みました
自分の想像以上に、悠太くんがこの作品を、自分にとってもファンにとっても満足のいくように、本当に全力で考えて作り上げたことが分かった
韓国と日本とリモートで作品を作り上げるのは、とても集中力を必要とする作業だし、悠太くんの中でブレないイメージがあったから出来たことだと思う
あと、ライブを想定して音楽を作っていくやり方が悠太くんらしいな、と思った
観客の存在が、音楽のラストピースを埋めて、もっとエモーショナルに生まれ変わる感覚を知っている人なんだろうな
ビハインドやインタビューで、彼の言葉やふるまいを知れば知るほど、信頼の出来るアーティストだと思う
(こんなに真摯に作り上げた作品を、ちゃんとプロモートしなかったSMに対する信頼は、この先一生回復することは無いけどな)

author: @Diana5745
text: Yuta sets him apart from the rest of NCT going for a rock vibe. This album was so creative but so very much Yuta. My favs. from SM always gets the short end of the usual treatment of its idols, i.e. f(x) was always treated unfairly with less promotion and less support than Girls Generation. Their xenophobic tendencies shows that their artists can only excel once they leave this crappy company. EXO C had to combine with EXO K even though EXO C had started with a more popular response (they won an music award before the EXO K team). Yuta being the first Japanese idol for SM is especially heartbreaking since he always promotes NCT when doing solo activities like his talk show. Although he loves his NCT members he will never grow to his full potential by staying with SM, hope he goes soon.

author: @fraam.168
text:
We finally have the behind the scene! 😍 He literally put everything in it. Everything looked so detailed. Even though it seems to have been recorded in a rush - had that feeling -, you finally posted and fixed one of the 99 things you did wrong like not promoting him properly. People didn’t even know he released an album. The different and disgusting treatment he received compared to the others is disgusting. SM and Avex going back and forth on his profile to take credits. Idk what is happening but we can see it. 
But he’s truly a rockstar. He accomplished so many things and he will achieve many others in the future. The album sold out and you don’t even dare to restock it. Do it now please! I have to remind you that he’s the only one that got two grammy articles about his solo debut and you didn’t let him have an interview (cuz i bet he didn’t even know about it). Please SM, fix the other stuff and don’t get credit when him and the japanese staff did all bay themselves. I hope there will be other behind the scenes or contents (like some clips are missing from the album pictures 
for example yuta for the existential version where he lays on the wall near the window, the bath one… what about the photobook behind?) with yuta or with only yuta! He deserve to get all the things he have been excluded or mistreated. YUTA YOU ARE SO LOVED! YOU NEED TO KNOW THAT! KISSES FROM ITALIA 🇮🇹  WE NEED A SOLO TOUR IN EUROPE! Everyone loved his album kpop fans, jpop fans and people who listen to rock too! Open your eyes, SM! I have to say this is the best album out of all of them cuz he attracted so many people outside this fandom and the lyrics SO GOOD!
